{"tid":1127525,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日皇明仁男孫書桌被放菜刀 警方︰有人喬裝工人","createTime":"2019-04-27T07:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T10:00:56.000Z","uid":3090,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"96d0d6522d7f5e4cfbe7b7ea96b03aaea1e024be","tid":1127525,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hs74oSi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHs74oSi.png&h=01683b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n御茶水女子大學附屬中學，紅圈為悠仁(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n日皇明仁將於本月30日退位，他的孫子、12歲的悠仁在學校的座位被人放置兩把菜刀，警方正進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，有人在悠仁的課室座位上放了兩把菜刀，當時學生去上戶外教學課，教室裏沒有人。翻查閉路電視錄影後，發現有可疑人士喬裝成工人進入校園，又指他進入學校時並沒有登記。<br />\n<br />\n悠仁本月8日起就讀於文京區御茶水女子大學附屬中學一年级，他是日皇明仁次子文仁親王的兒子，也是日皇的唯一男孫，太子德仁5月1日即位為日皇後，悠仁就是皇位繼承順位第二位。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社／中央社／《日本時報》"},{"pid":"32aa71751d753cc2466e5312dce7e81375edcdf0","tid":1127525,"uid":3241,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"支那間諜所為"},{"pid":"83906bc9229e752ab566bc9aced93809001a0fd4","tid":1127525,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"宮本武藏"},{"pid":"d8c9fe77d3bc4e7b3d4b778b027141c9e3c21a0c","tid":1127525,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"女校男生"},{"pid":"98506a18ca6dce6ceb8b9415c00ffff1e9bb15ae","tid":1127525,"uid":24310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8c9fe77d3bc4e7b3d4b778b027141c9e3c21a0c","tid":1127525,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"女校男生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T08:13:30.000Z","msg":"女子大學附屬中學唔一定女校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39926da070a8d3251cfb6cc8398615ca3139e16","tid":1127525,"uid":42767,